# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#AuthorisedRepresentativeRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#AuthorisedRepresentativeRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#AuthorisedRepresentativeRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#AuthorisedRepresentativeRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A natural or legal person established in the EU mandated by\n         the manufacturer to act on their behalf."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#AuthorisedRepresentativeRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Authorised Representative"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#AuthorisedRepresentativeRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "ESPR Article 2(43)."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ConsumerRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ConsumerRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ConsumerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ConsumerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An end user with read access to public and use-phase DPP data,\n         including product identification and energy efficiency data."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ConsumerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Consumer"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#CustomsAuthorityRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#CustomsAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#CustomsAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#CustomsAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A customs enforcement authority with read access to\n         product identification and certification data at border control."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#CustomsAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Customs Authority"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#DistributorRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#DistributorRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#DistributorRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#DistributorRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An entity in the supply chain that makes a product available\n         on the market other than the manufacturer or importer."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#DistributorRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Distributor"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#DistributorRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "ESPR Article 2(45)."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A role defined under ESPR Article 2(46) with specific DPP data\n         rights and obligations."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Economic Operator"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ImporterRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ImporterRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ImporterRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ImporterRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An entity that places products manufactured outside the EU\n         on the EU market and assumes ESPR obligations."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ImporterRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Importer"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ImporterRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "ESPR Article 2(44)."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MaintenanceTechnicianRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MaintenanceTechnicianRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MaintenanceTechnicianRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ServiceProviderRole> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MaintenanceTechnicianRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A certified technician performing repair or maintenance with\n         read access to use-and-maintenance and repairability data."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MaintenanceTechnicianRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Maintenance Technician"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ManufacturerRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ManufacturerRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ManufacturerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#EconomicOperator> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ManufacturerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The entity that manufactures the product and is the primary\n         DPP data owner with full read/write access to all modules."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ManufacturerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Manufacturer"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ManufacturerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "ESPR Article 2(42)."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MarketSurveillanceAuthorityRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MarketSurveillanceAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MarketSurveillanceAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MarketSurveillanceAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A national authority with full read access to all DPP\n         modules per Regulation (EU) 2019/1020."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MarketSurveillanceAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Market Surveillance Authority"@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#MarketSurveillanceAuthorityRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "ESPR Article 11(b); Regulation (EU) 2019/1020."@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RecyclerRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RecyclerRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RecyclerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RecyclerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An entity processing products at end-of-life with read access\n         to material composition and disassembly instruction data."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RecyclerRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Recycler"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A public authority with statutory rights to access DPP data\n         for market surveillance or customs enforcement."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#RegulatoryAuthority> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Regulatory Authority"@en .
