# http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ServiceProviderRole
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ServiceProviderRole> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ServiceProviderRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://w3id.org/dpp/access-control#Role> .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ServiceProviderRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An entity providing after-sales services such as repair,\n         maintenance, or refurbishment."@en .
<http://w3id.org/dpp/roles#ServiceProviderRole> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Service Provider"@en .
